  HAMER 2026 will be held in two locations:
  <ul>
    <li>Day 1 (May 8, 2026): <a href='https://maps.app.goo.gl/QWHfCvWu3nhBN9xC9'>Consulate General of Greece in Boston</a>, located at <strong>86 Beacon St, Boston, MA 02108</strong>
    <li>Day 2 (May 9, 2026): <a href='https://maps.app.goo.gl/fVJHXwCKfdtGZ7to6'>MIT Room 66-110</a>, located at <b>25 Ames St, Cambridge, MA 02139</b>
